  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creator of <strong>Chicken Feet</strong> comes <strong>Below Nowhere</strong>, a first-person survival horror game about life, memories, second chances, and the Meat Man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/c1b754d100a8d059b295a951ca499be7.poster.avif?t=1774218956\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/c1b754d100a8d059b295a951ca499be7.webm?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/c1b754d100a8d059b295a951ca499be7.mp4?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped deep underground during humanity’s final war, you are pulled into a shifting reality built from memories that aren’t yours. Each place is different, yet they all share a tragic similarity: dried bloodshed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MEET THE MEAT MAN</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You aren't alone. The Meat Man feasts on evil and death.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A trickster, the animalistic Meat Man likes to play with his food.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Meat Man enjoys causing you pain and suffering more than anything.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/5c677db75a34ddd17d8afa129dbd16a8.poster.avif?t=1774218956\" width=606 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/5c677db75a34ddd17d8afa129dbd16a8.webm?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/5c677db75a34ddd17d8afa129dbd16a8.mp4?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPAIR YOUR BODY PARTS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Meat Man will try to rip you apart piece by piece. Individual body parts can be injured, altering your abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When heavily damaged, be wise! Medicine bottles are scarce. Be smart about the body parts you heal first.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your body is entirely exhausted, any extra injury will be fatal.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/97aa2cf701e9a1e18b4c667a86645f7d.poster.avif?t=1774218956\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/97aa2cf701e9a1e18b4c667a86645f7d.webm?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/97aa2cf701e9a1e18b4c667a86645f7d.mp4?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A PLACE BELOW NOWHERE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend into the darkness and voyage through strange memories that aren't yours.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vicious Meat Man will be hunting you. Use the environment to your advantage and hide in the darkness where he can't see you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious white glowing doorways mark your escape. Reach them to be spared by the Meat Man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have no way of defending yourself. Your only choices are to run, hide, or die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features an original dark ambient soundtrack composed by The Nomad Communion.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Built with Unreal Engine 5.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/0f34660ff658677a27358a034ffb2b0f.avif?t=1774218956\" width=616 height=149 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creator of <strong>Chicken Feet</strong> comes <strong>Below Nowhere</strong>, a first-person survival horror game about life, memories, second chances, and the Meat Man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/c1b754d100a8d059b295a951ca499be7.poster.avif?t=1774218956\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/c1b754d100a8d059b295a951ca499be7.webm?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/c1b754d100a8d059b295a951ca499be7.mp4?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped deep underground during humanity’s final war, you are pulled into a shifting reality built from memories that aren’t yours. Each place is different, yet they all share a tragic similarity: dried bloodshed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MEET THE MEAT MAN</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You aren't alone. The Meat Man feasts on evil and death.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A trickster, the animalistic Meat Man likes to play with his food.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Meat Man enjoys causing you pain and suffering more than anything.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/5c677db75a34ddd17d8afa129dbd16a8.poster.avif?t=1774218956\" width=606 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/5c677db75a34ddd17d8afa129dbd16a8.webm?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/5c677db75a34ddd17d8afa129dbd16a8.mp4?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPAIR YOUR BODY PARTS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Meat Man will try to rip you apart piece by piece. Individual body parts can be injured, altering your abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When heavily damaged, be wise! Medicine bottles are scarce. Be smart about the body parts you heal first.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your body is entirely exhausted, any extra injury will be fatal.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/97aa2cf701e9a1e18b4c667a86645f7d.poster.avif?t=1774218956\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/97aa2cf701e9a1e18b4c667a86645f7d.webm?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/97aa2cf701e9a1e18b4c667a86645f7d.mp4?t=1774218956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A PLACE BELOW NOWHERE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend into the darkness and voyage through strange memories that aren't yours.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vicious Meat Man will be hunting you. Use the environment to your advantage and hide in the darkness where he can't see you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious white glowing doorways mark your escape. Reach them to be spared by the Meat Man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have no way of defending yourself. Your only choices are to run, hide, or die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features an original dark ambient soundtrack composed by The Nomad Communion.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Built with Unreal Engine 5.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569280/extras/0f34660ff658677a27358a034ffb2b0f.avif?t=1774218956\" width=616 height=149 /></span></p>",
